The paper discusses machine learning in adversarial settings, specifically the vulnerability of classifiers to evasion attacks. This topic is closely related to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer security (cs.CR), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
